menu "Tab5 audio device arbitration"

    config MQJS_TAB5_AUDIO_DEVICE_SELFTEST
        bool "Boot-time audio_device token self-test"
        depends on MQJS_TAB5_AUDIO
        default n
        help
            Exercise the audio_device P1 exclusive-token layer on real
            hardware shortly after boot: submit two overlapping requests so
            the first is granted immediately and the second queues, play a
            short beep through each granted token (audio_request ->
            audio_stream_write -> audio_stream_finish), and log the
            grant/queue/dispatch sequence plus audio_tab5 stats. Verifies
            the manager task, token validation, and backend hand-off without
            touching the existing tone/WAV producers. Leave off in shipping
            builds.

endmenu
